hopobject.body: Will I have to work shifts? dr s reilly - crown medical centre taunton "The problem I have with this is that teaching hospitals, which did poorly in this report, tend to have more complicated patients," said Dr. Richard Besser, chief health medical editor for ABC News. "More complicated patients will tend to be in the hospital longer. Community hospitals, which did better in this report, often refer their more complicated cases elsewhere."
